          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; 99 lives -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Hold L1 And R2 And press the following O O O O Triangle square and square</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Full Scare Meter -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>While Playing hold L1+R1 and press circle(3),Square(2),X,Triangle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Max Health (not infinite) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Hold L1 & R1 while holding press circle 3 times, square, triangle, X, triangle while playing the game</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite Lives -
