			<br>&nbsp; Movie theater Fully Open -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80010118 FFFF<br>8001011A FFFF</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; All Medals -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800100C8 6363<br>800100CA 6363<br>800100CC 6363<br>800100CE 6363<br>800100D0 6363<br>300100D2 0063<br>300100C7 0063<br>800100D4 FFFF<br>800100D6 FFFF<br>800100D8 FFFF<br>800100DA FFFF<br>800100DC FFFF<br>800100DE FFFF</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; All stages -
